I"r<ul>
  <li>Depending on the number of olympic users, the teams will have a size from 2 to 4 people.</li>
  <li>The competition consists on <strong>[?] problems</strong> (in arithmetic, number theory, analysis and algebra.)</li>
  <li>There will be two kind of problems: <strong>result-like</strong> problems and <strong>proof-like</strong> problems. Below you can find examples of both kinds. The following table resumes the possible marks:</li>
</ul>

